{"tid":987830,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"戒煙互助，支持，分享","createTime":"2019-01-19T15:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T07:52:49.000Z","uid":124436,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"158bbc0f945010dba52c6fe8df085a8568fbb19b","tid":987830,"uid":124436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:18:29.000Z","msg":"食左 20幾年煙，十年前戒過一次 , 但1年後再次食返<br />\n<br />\n最近發現身體差左，決心再戒多一次<br />\n<br />\n但發覺今次難度高左好多，今日，第四日出現後遺症 勁左好多<br />\n<br />\n頭暈，頭痛，集中唔到，口味改變，嘔心感覺，好易累，成日想訓<br />\n<br />\n要不食好多甜野，先可以舒緩下<br />\n<br />\n大家戒煙 又有乜心得？ 有乜難？ 大家互助支持下"},{"pid":"dcdff0fc2ed5e32cdbf132868913be8e6e79b062","tid":987830,"uid":124436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:44:47.000Z","msg":"今日第五日， 感覺都係差唔多<br />\n<br />\n頭好暈，好難集中精神"},{"pid":"8478871bb833f8f59f3ff1a2be87326dfe0f6579","tid":987830,"uid":189214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"加油啊 巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104715b490480a06fddb98f4485ebf87ecc62319","tid":987830,"uid":4596,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:56:59.000Z","msg":"支持呀點樣都要戒咗佢ah 幾時戒都好 總之戒咗個mortality rate就會跌㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:喺醫院見到好多阿伯COPD 同佢地拍痰見到佢哋真係好辛苦"},{"pid":"6f5c84562b72b88a8a3c7df4f908b25c3bf8f046","tid":987830,"uid":124436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:15:24.000Z","msg":"第六日 <br />\n<br />\n好似無之前咁頭暈，但出現喉嚨乾，喉嚨痕，簡中會有咳，有淡<br />\n<br />\n要多飲水"},{"pid":"9503e5e8f4d9599d0df77d9ef55bf9d52a576fa1","tid":987830,"uid":227691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:12:24.000Z","msg":"食咗廿幾年會唔會好難戒<br />\n加油巴打，為咗你嘅健康着想"},{"pid":"a45f45868a2b7e9385e4c7cd11bdced3488842d9","tid":987830,"uid":227539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"等車時, 冇野做時, 去飲野時都好想食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食左5年, 戒左2日, 不過一直唔承認自己有煙癮<br />\n加油呀巴打"},{"pid":"f2668f2dc31ae84c9722fe02085e510b5761aba5","tid":987830,"uid":200270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄啊! 堅持落去就冇事"},{"pid":"e4e1c265ec802fc1d4e4ea924ea646988532a671","tid":987830,"uid":231523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"食支煙支持你"},{"pid":"6b3d7a2ee016677a04b3b6400ad9900e3bc55118","tid":987830,"uid":150651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rJajKtW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrJajKtW.png&h=318a4629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點點燈先啦老同"},{"pid":"e9ef458f081f3d8c2a1e11164f2ccd545de17c42","tid":987830,"uid":21883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"唔覺唔覺已經食左十年<br />\n最長一次戒過一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有無試戒煙貼"},{"pid":"e4836745f9cc56df97d7abda084376c3dc11baec","tid":987830,"uid":20492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:43:01.000Z","msg":"戒左兩個月 聞到就想嘔，<br />\n由真煙到去食iqos 都已經唔想食真煙<br />\n一日把心一橫掉哂啲機同煙蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72beaac0aeda38e03d5fa82ce68109d205b2d4d7","tid":987830,"uid":131017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:07:31.000Z","msg":"食左十幾年, 想戒<br />\n加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b794ec4cbd5ef2b3d93843b32331c6defed149","tid":987830,"uid":193476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"食左廿年煙個肺係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sixeBeq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsixeBeq.png&h=d8cfb5e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53edb67abc91aeb23ba86c704b5f699ca61df4c0","tid":987830,"uid":124436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9ef458f081f3d8c2a1e11164f2ccd545de17c42","tid":987830,"uid":21883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"唔覺唔覺已經食左十年<br />\n最長一次戒過一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有無試戒煙貼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:08:58.000Z","msg":"無用戒煙貼"},{"pid":"2ce6b132b8c4e351436fddeb3b42f80ccfb95668","tid":987830,"uid":124436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:11:27.000Z","msg":"第 7 日 <br />\n<br />\n感覺不錯，之前既後遺症都慢慢減輕或消失<br />\n<br />\n身邊有人食煙，都無想食既意欲<br />\n<br />\n聞到煙味覺得好臭<br />\n<br />\n相信今次戒煙應該會成功！"},{"pid":"edc7100e78314f07d8914a531961dfa780226ea9","tid":987830,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53edb67abc91aeb23ba86c704b5f699ca61df4c0","tid":987830,"uid":124436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9ef458f081f3d8c2a1e11164f2ccd545de17c42","tid":987830,"uid":21883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"唔覺唔覺已經食左十年<br />\n最長一次戒過一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有無試戒煙貼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:08:58.000Z","msg":"無用戒煙貼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:41:30.000Z","msg":"用啦<br />\n我爸爸食左40年煙 佢都戒到<br />\n你都得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d442966c375f1fae68708c04825e8186f34e2b09","tid":987830,"uid":23804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"巴打加油，我分享下我經驗:<br />\n2018年9月1日買咗電子煙，唔係煙草果種，係VAPE，食冇丁煙油，頭一個星期係最難頂，跟住頭一個月慢慢開始習慣VAPE，到第二個月開始VAPE都少食，跟住到目前已經VAPE都冇食，但有時候非常失落時會有念頭想食下，所以keep住部VAPE機，最多食2啖，共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}